mca <- MCA(
  d[,c(
    "Attr",
    "Vinf_Cop",
    "VM_MOD",
    "AUTHOR",
    "DIST_OBJ_PRED"
    )], 
  quali.sup = 4,
  quanti.sup = 5,
  method="Burt",
  graph = F)

fviz_screeplot(
  mca,
  addlabels = TRUE,
  ylim = c(0, 80),
  barfill="#1B9E77",
  barcolor="#1B9E77",
  main="Eigenvalues"
  ) + 
  theme_get()

mca.plot <- plot(
  mca,
  invisible = "ind",

  ) +
  theme_get()
